1777664603773326	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEywQw		item.update	bn-3471	{"field":"description","value":"Validated first step for bn-5kad.\n\nCurrent inventory on 2026-05-01 reports 522 `Command::new(\"git\")` substring matches across `crates src tests benches`: 453 outside top-level `tests/`, 69 inside top-level `tests/`. This count includes `StdCommand::new(\"git\")` and in-file crate test modules, so the next audit must classify each hit as:\n\n- production replace-now\n- production temporary remote carveout\n- crate-local test fixture/setup\n- top-level integration test fixture/setup\n- intentional git-compatibility assertion\n\nDeliverables:\n\n1. A checked-in inventory document or generated report with counts by file and classification.\n2. Updated bn-5kad description if counts move materially.\n3. A recommended implementation order, keeping hot-path working-copy/capture/merge/resolve ahead of init-only and test-only cleanup.\n4. A definition of done for permanent push/fetch carveouts so they are not confused with forgotten subprocesses."}	blake3:9UgvzBdHlygRtca5m_mPlbKn6Knyc_iPw1J7DiTexK8
1777664603799019	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEywgw		item.update	bn-5k0g	{"field":"description","value":"Validated scope: `working_copy.rs` has 38 matches and `capture.rs` has 20 matches in the 2026-05-01 inventory.\n\nReplace production git CLI calls in `crates/maw-cli/src/workspace/working_copy.rs` and `crates/maw-cli/src/workspace/capture.rs` where practical. Prioritize operations that run during merge cleanup, dirty default replay, destroy capture, and rewrite safety:\n\n- dirty path/status discovery\n- index add/reset/cleanup\n- stash create/apply behavior or equivalent snapshot primitives\n- reading file content at commits\n- checkout/reset of target refs\n- conflict-marker detection support that currently shells to git\n\nAssumptions to validate during implementation:\n\n- Some counted calls are in in-file tests and should move to shared test helpers or be classified test-only.\n- Replacing stash semantics may require new maw-git primitives rather than direct one-for-one gix calls.\n- Recovery guarantees are more important than reducing the count quickly; keep data-loss regressions green."}	blake3:-_2JFj0lun357qfzJFzQ_9tgtDnotY8BGA6sAfqhBy4
1777664603824006	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEywww		item.update	bn-2j9f	{"field":"description","value":"Validated scope: `crates/maw-cli/src/workspace/recover.rs` has 28 matches in the 2026-05-01 inventory, not the older 21-call count.\n\nRemove production git CLI use from recovery snapshot inspection and restore paths where gix object traversal can provide equivalent behavior. Primary targets:\n\n- `git show <oid>:<path>` style file reads\n- `git grep` / snapshot content search\n- tree/object existence checks\n- restore checkout paths that can use backend/worktree primitives\n\nPreserve:\n\n- binary-safe `--show` output\n- path traversal validation\n- paths containing colons\n- destroyed-workspace search behavior\n- recovery audit events\n- all existing recover/destroy integration tests\n\nSeparate in-file tests from production calls before reporting count reduction."}	blake3:ZREsUgFUByuhMH9AbzgmytcsHePiRYGjRA9hEd7Gi4w
1777664603850743	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyxAw		item.update	bn-14gc	{"field":"description","value":"Validated scope: `crates/maw-cli/src/v2_init.rs` is still the largest single file with 55 matches in the 2026-05-01 inventory.\n\nReplace initialization-time git CLI calls with maw-git/gix primitives where practical. Scope includes:\n\n- repo creation/bootstrap and bare-mode configuration\n- branch/HEAD discovery\n- worktree registration and repair checks\n- ref/bootstrap reads and writes\n- brownfield migration status/cleanup checks\n- root tracked-file removal and untracked-file warnings\n\nAssumptions to validate:\n\n- Some initialization operations may still need git CLI until equivalent maw-git primitives exist; create those primitives only when reusable.\n- Many hits may be in in-file greenfield/brownfield tests; classify them separately.\n- Preserve idempotent brownfield migration behavior and the existing v2_init test matrix."}	blake3:2riM3CMHSXeKoFrK4GFm-wuqv-UZftLoED22XSA2FPc
1777664603878295	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyxQw		item.update	bn-p5z5	{"field":"description","value":"Validated scope: `crates/maw-core/src/backend/git.rs` has 35 matches in the 2026-05-01 inventory.\n\nEliminate production `Command::new(\"git\")` calls in the core Git workspace backend by moving behavior onto maw-git/GitRepo primitives. Focus on:\n\n- workspace create/list/status/destroy\n- worktree registration and cleanup\n- base epoch and HEAD discovery\n- name-status/diff/status parsing currently delegated to porcelain\n- file status and dirty-count behavior\n\nImplementation constraint: add missing primitives at the maw-git boundary when they are reusable by other bn-5kad children, especially v2_init, working_copy, and sync/resolve. Protect behavior with backend tests and existing workspace lifecycle/status suites."}	blake3:egf8OMaid5ul0okQt9wBouhS2JURU-b4NDeoIf0Fvio
1777664603909150	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyxgw		item.update	bn-3005	{"field":"description","value":"Validated scope from the 2026-05-01 inventory:\n\n- `crates/maw-core/src/refs.rs`: 11 matches\n- `crates/maw-core/src/oplog/write.rs`: 13 matches\n- `crates/maw-core/src/oplog/read.rs`: 7 matches\n- `crates/maw-core/src/oplog/checkpoint.rs`: 6 matches\n- `crates/maw-core/src/oplog/view.rs`: 1 match\n\nReplace ref/object plumbing shellouts such as update-ref, rev-parse, cat-file, hash-object, and checkpoint object reads/writes with gix-backed primitives while preserving:\n\n- compare-and-swap ref semantics\n- oplog ancestry checks\n- damaged-chain warning/repair behavior\n- checkpoint materialization and recovery behavior\n\nThis task should expose stable low-level helpers for other migration tasks instead of duplicating gix object/ref code."}	blake3:h1wGfvrX5PLlULtst-v6D2EVArRU-7G4zwOCOR8YSl8
1777664603936019	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyxww		item.update	bn-3lcl	{"field":"description","value":"Validated scope from the 2026-05-01 inventory includes more than the old collect-phase residuals:\n\n- `src/merge/collect.rs`: 11 matches\n- `crates/maw-core/src/merge/build.rs`: 9 matches\n- `crates/maw-cli/src/workspace/merge.rs`: 9 matches\n- related phase helpers: `src/merge/build_phase.rs` (7), `src/merge/quarantine.rs` (6), `src/merge/prepare.rs` (3), `src/merge/commit.rs` (2), `src/merge/validate.rs` (2), plus smaller merge helper files\n\nFinish removing git CLI calls from merge-engine and merge-orchestration paths after bn-2jpn. Prefer shared GitRepo tree/blob/diff/commit helpers so merge collect/build logic avoids porcelain parsing and handles non-ASCII paths correctly.\n\nThis is size L, not M: split further if implementation starts touching both core merge engine and CLI merge orchestration in one patch."}	blake3:84NE02xEc-5rGrh7TUp0peO-n8iGV2qtWmULZM64vNQ
