1777664603996873	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyyQw		item.update	bn-28ky	{"field":"description","value":"Validated scope from the 2026-05-01 inventory:\n\n- `crates/maw-cli/src/transport.rs`: 17 matches\n- `crates/maw-cli/src/push.rs`: 11 matches\n- `crates/maw-cli/src/release.rs`: 5 matches\n- `crates/maw-cli/src/lfs_push.rs`: 5 matches\n- `crates/maw-git/src/push_impl.rs`: 2 matches\n\nAudit transport and publishing code with a strict carveout boundary:\n\n- Keep actual push/fetch protocol subprocesses only where gix-protocol is not yet a reliable replacement.\n- Replace surrounding local operations such as rev-list/counts, tag/ref discovery, remote-ref inspection, status checks, and object reads where maw-git/gix primitives exist or can be added.\n- Centralize remaining remote-operation shellouts behind a clearly named wrapper and document each retained call.\n\nDo not treat all transport.rs calls as permanent carveouts; many are local setup/test helper calls."}	blake3:Xxsq3mi2002Wgw737PjWK682ItIk6UjGh2-AMmy3ONE
